## False Positives in QA Report (NOT actual bugs)

| Issue | Why It's Not a Bug |
|---|---|
| **ISSUE-004** (Attendance duplicate) | API already uses `findOneAndUpdate` with upsert — updates existing record instead of failing |
| **ISSUE-009** (Test result dead-end) | Page already has a "← Back to Tests" `Link` at line 83 |
| **ISSUE-024** (Test no auto-submit) | Timer already calls [handleSubmit(true)](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/complete-profile/page.tsx#124-147) when `t <= 1` at line 88 |

