## Known Limitations (Not Fixed — Out of Scope)
- **ISSUE-019:** Overdue documents are permanently locked. No extension request mechanism exists. This is a design gap, not a bug.
- **ISSUE-016:** Dual fee systems ([StudentFee](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/StudentFee.ts#11-31) vs [FeePayment](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/FeePayment.ts#13-33)) remain. Unifying requires data migration — not a fix-only task.
- **ISSUE-021:** Public library uses old [Library](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Library.ts#3-15) model while admin uses [LibraryDocument](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/LibraryDocument.ts#3-18). Requires model consolidation.
- Pre-existing TS errors in [tests/unit/security/concurrency.test.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/tests/unit/security/concurrency.test.ts) (not related to our changes)

